Forget trendy toys - all one little girl wanted for Christmas was her military father home early from Afghanistan. And this week, that wish came true. 

A camera crew captured the heartwarming homecoming surprise at BB Owen Elementary School in Texas on Tuesday.

Kennedy Shaw was filmed as she got up on stage  to unwrap a giant bow-wrapped present she 'won' during a rigged raffle.

Footage shows her tackling the gift while her peers watch on, then all of a sudden her father jumps out and she can barely contain her excitement.

