Shocked: Sgt. Jayson Shaw got teachers at Kennedy's school to wrap him up in a big box - his daughter was then called up to the stage to open the parcel after 'winning' it in a rigged raffle

Dad's home! The 5th grader could hardly contain her excitement when she saw what was inside 

